              "iaja": "A",
              "text": "The thesis is a mix-shift trade. Hexatronic is pivoting from a commoditised FTTH supplier (where it has ~1% US market share vs Corning/Prysmian/Dura-Line) to a services-led DC and Harsh Environment player. The pivot is measurable: DC+HE revenue share 35% → 40% in one year, EBITA share ~60%. The risk is that the hyperscaler build-out has 'boom-and-bust' characteristics identical to the FTTH cycle that just broke — trading one cyclical trap for another."
            },
            {
              "type": "bullet_group",
              "items": [
                {
                  "iaja": "J",
                  "text": "PRIMARY driver: DC segment scaling to SEK 3bn by 2028 — the fulcrum. Proof point is Q4-25 +62% organic.",
                  "sub": [
                    {
                      "iaja": "I",
                      "text": "Cloud now ~40% of DC segment sales; hyperscaler concentration is the obvious risk."
                    },
                    {
                      "iaja": "I",
                      "text": "Management targets 3-6 acquisitions/year at 5-7x EBITDA, EV <EUR 50m each."
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "iaja": "J",
                  "text": "SECONDARY driver: BEAD programme materialisation — triggers legacy FTTH recovery.",
                  "sub": [
                    {
                      "iaja": "A",
                      "text": "$42.5bn US subsidy stalled. Inflection now H2-26 per management."
                    },
                    {
                      "iaja": "A",
                      "text": "Rule changes made it 'technology-neutral' — LEO/FWA now eligible. 74% of early-state allocations still go to fibre."
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "iaja": "J",
                  "text": "TERTIARY driver: New CEO Rikard Fröberg execution (from March 2025). Nascent Corporate Change input — too early to rate.",
                  "sub": [
                    {
                      "iaja": "I",
                      "text": "Ex-Ansell — international/US experience but no prior fibre/connectivity role."
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "prose",
              "iaja": "A",
              "ratings": [
                {
                  "grade": "B",
                  "attr": "setup quality"
